---
description: Do not assume unused services
globs: ["**/*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx,json,sql,md,mdc,yml,yaml}"]
alwaysApply: true
---

Before suggesting architecture, integrations, env vars, storage, streaming, or refactors:
- check the existing repository context first
- do not assume Supabase, Apwrite, Railway, DigitalOcean, Ghost, Netlify, Firebase, or other services are used
- do not mention unused services as defaults
- do not recommend migrations unless explicitly requested

If a service is not already present in the code or explicitly requested by the user, do not introduce it.
